    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# 🚀 AI Product Mockup Generator\n\nGenerate professional product mockups from a single product image.\n\n## Workflow\n\n1. Upload a product image.\n2. Select a visual style (Editorial, Cinematic, Fashion, or any custom style).\n3. AI creates 3 unique scene prompts while preserving the exact product identity.\n4. Flux Kontext generates 3 photorealistic mockups.\n5. Generated images are downloaded and automatically uploaded to Google Drive.\n\n✅ Easily extendable with additional visual styles.\n✅ Product identity is preserved across all generated images.",
        "height": 416,
        "width": 752
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -448,
        -656
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "b38454e4-86f8-4402-8e0f-14f892afa45a",
      "name": "Sticky Note4"
    },
